### Health Check
GET http://localhost:11434

### List Models
GET http://localhost:11434/api/tags

### Chat - Single Message
POST http://localhost:11434/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "llama3",
  "messages": [
    {"role": "user", "content": "Hello, how are you?"}
  ],
  "stream": false
}

### Chat - With System Prompt
POST http://localhost:11434/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "llama3",
  "messages": [
    {"role": "system", "content": "You are a helpful Java developer assistant."},
    {"role": "user", "content": "Explain the difference between HashMap and ConcurrentHashMap."}
  ],
  "stream": false
}

### Chat - Multi-turn Conversation
POST http://localhost:11434/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "llama3",
  "messages": [
    {"role": "user", "content": "What is Spring Boot?"},
    {"role": "assistant", "content": "Spring Boot is a framework that simplifies building production-ready Spring applications."},
    {"role": "user", "content": "How do I create a REST controller?"}
  ],
  "stream": false
}

### Generate - Single Prompt (no conversation)
POST http://localhost:11434/api/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "llama3",
  "prompt": "Write a Java method that reverses a string",
  "stream": false
}

### Generate - With Temperature
POST http://localhost:11434/api/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "llama3",
  "prompt": "Give me 3 creative project names for a payment API",
  "stream": false,
  "options": {
    "temperature": 0.9
  }
}

### Pull a Model
POST http://localhost:11434/api/pull
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "llama3",
  "stream": false
}

### Show Model Info
POST http://localhost:11434/api/show
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "llama3"
}

### Embeddings
POST http://localhost:11434/api/embeddings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "llama3",
  "prompt": "Ollama is a tool for running LLMs locally"
}
